<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> frewnd <expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan> rate, die
                        nehst bey <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                            durch<expan>lewchtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> von unsers gnedigen
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> herczog Stepfans
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan>
<expan>brud<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> sein, wol
                        gesagt, wie sich ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> in
                                <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und gen in <expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        beweiset hab, des wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiss
                                <expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan> und williklich
                            <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>zu verdiene<ex>n</ex></expan>. Also <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        wir zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>durchl<ex>euhtikeit</ex></expan> Hannsen
                            <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir befolhen
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, von <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> zu reden. Und
                            <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr <expan>fürstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        gnade <expan>dienstl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und mit fleiss, was
                                <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> Hanns <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        in bona <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> credencie.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<add><expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan></add>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Petri ad
                            <expan>vinc<ex>u</ex>la</expan>.</ab>
